<hymn_number>247</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvel in &quot;Sesum leh sana,
 A lul,&quot; ti'n a hawl viel ui,
 Mahleh a lulnau chun Pielgal a tun zo puoi,
 Van hawihnan Pielgal a salhvak
 Ziechuh ahi ka gen nuom.

[V2]
 A chanchin gen thiem leng Aw thangvan khu,
 A hawih zie gen thiem leng aw ka Lal lenna;
 Mitin in suilung in gulh leu,
 Van In nuomah hung lawi leu.

[V3]
 2. Khawvel lopina leh hawihna,
 Ni tam tak a liem zo tai;
 Mahleh van hawihna chu, khangthak tamtak beih nung
 A thakin a hawih deuh deuh hi
 Ziechuh ahi gen takpen.

[V4]
 3. Van In hawih lopi leh sang chu
 Kawt chu khuna lut ahi
 Aw Kalvari tang leh, Bethlehem bawng In ah
 Kuol ding leh Kross A put ding khan
 Kuo Lal puon tawh a chieh dem ?

[V5]
 4. Bangtik leh ka vaihna gam leh
 Ka kahna gam hi beiin
 Thangvan gam lopi leh hawih gen senloh gam lun
 A bukim in a hung tung dem
 A ngaiin nau bang ka kap.</lyrics>
<title>Sesum leh Sana Sangin</title>
</song>